lead_paragraph: Real Madrid coach Zinedine Zidane is set be without three of his  main forwards for Saturday's trip to Eibar after Cristiano Ronaldo missed training on Friday with an ankle knock, joining the suspended Gareth Bale and Alvaro Morata on the sidelines.
